      <p style="font-size:18px;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);max-width:540px;margin:0 0 28px;">Hickman is one of the fastest-growing communities in Lancaster County, and a lot of that growth means big unfinished basements waiting for a legal bedroom. We install code-compliant egress windows for Hickman homeowners and back every job with a free written estimate.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;">
