<section style="padding:72px 24px 40px;"><div style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;"><div class="rich"><p>Hickman has grown fast over the last two decades, and most of that growth shows up as newer construction in the Norris School District draw area with full, unfinished basements. Those basements are a great head start on a finished bedroom or living space, but Nebraska code still requires a proper <a href="/egress-window-installation-lincoln/">egress window</a> before that space can legally count as a bedroom.</p><p>We work with homeowners throughout Hickman on new <a href="/egress-window-installation-lincoln/">egress window installation</a>, <a href="/egress-window-replacement-lincoln/">egress window replacement</a>, and <a href="/window-well-installation-lincoln/">window well installation</a>. Every job starts with a free written estimate, and we're licensed, insured, and available 24/7 for inspection deadlines and closing timelines.</p></div></div></section>
<section style="padding:0 24px 64px;"><div style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;">
    <span class="kicker">What We Do in Hickman</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading" style="font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);margin:0 0 28px;">Services for Hickman Properties</h2>
    <div class="feat-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:20px;">
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:10px;padding:26px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.05);">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 8px;">Egress Window Installation</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">Full cut-in service for Hickman's newer homes with large unfinished basements, so that extra square footage can become a legal bedroom or family room.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:10px;padding:26px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.05);">
